  "plot": [
    {
      "plot_summary": "The Armageddon Factor is the concluding serial of the Key to Time season. The Doctor and Romana I arrive on the twin planets Atrios and Zeos, embroiled in a devastating war orchestrated by the ominous Shadow, serving the Black Guardian. As the Doctor uncovers the final segment of the Key embedded in the Princess Astra, he faces seduction by absolute power but opts to scatter the segments, thwarting the Black Guardian's ambitions. Protecting the galaxy and Astra's world, the Doctor installs a randomizer in the TARDIS, ensuring unpredictable travels ahead."
    }
